//sad screen Feeling sad? Here are some tips to cool down! 01. Take a short walk outside and get some fresh air. 02. Listen to your favorite uplifting music. 03. Talk to a loved one about how you feel. 04. Write down your thoughts in a journal. 05. try a short meditation. 06. Drink a glass of water or have a healthy snack. 07. Watch something that makes you laugh. 08. Do a small act of kindness for someone else. 09. Engage in a hobby you enjoy. 10. Take a short break from screens.
//angry screen Feeling angry? Here are some tips to cool down! 01. Take a few deep breaths and count to ten. 02. Step away from the situation for a moment. 03. Go for a walk or do some light exercise. 04. Write down whatâ€™s making you angry. 05. Try a short meditation or breathing exercise. 06. Drink water or have a calming herbal tea. 07. Listen to soothing music or nature sounds. 08. Talk to a friend about your feelings calmly. 09. Engage in a hobby to release tension. 10. Practice mindfulness or a short relaxation exercise.
//anxious screen Feeling anxious? Here are some tips to cool down! 01. Take slow, deep breaths. 02. Count backwards from 100. 03. Stretch or do light exercise. 04. Drink a glass of water. 05. Step outside for fresh air. 06. Listen to calming music. 07. Write down your worries. 08. Practice a quick mindfulness exercise. 09. Talk to a friend or loved one. 10. Focus on something you enjoy.
